      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error beyond discretization and code verification is not required to be formally assessed at Model Risk Level 2 for this application. Residual convergence to 1e-5 for all equations was confirmed as a minimum quality check."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal use error analysis not required at MRL 2. Analyst training records and peer review of simulation setup are maintained internally but not submitted as structured evidence. The absence of pinned configuration values in deployment documentation represents an unaddressed use-error pathway not captured by this factor assessment."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
