      "rationale": "Formal equivalency analysis between validation input parameters and deployment input parameters not required at MRL 2. The COU does not specify constraints on solver configuration parameters (mesh size, time-step multiplier, damage threshold) that must be maintained between validation and deployment use, leaving a gap in parameter equivalency assurance."
